类 Bank_kid_control

java.lang.Object
Controller.bank.Bank_kid_control
所有已实现的接口:
RefreshListener
public class Bank_kid_control extends Object implements RefreshListener
The Bank_kid_control class manages the interaction between the bank GUI and the underlying data model for a child user. It handles user actions, such as editing saving goals and viewing account information.
